    <%- include('../includes/nav'); %>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <section class="hero">

            <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid mb-0">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
                        <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-6">
                            <h1 class="display-4">&#8220;Check your life along with the boxes&#8221;

                            </h1>

                            <p class="lead">Bring structure to your common day work and get A Sense Of Accomplishment
                                with TWello.</p>
                            <p class="lead"> Plan to Manage Time and to get all the Goals into Action</p>

                            <% if (!isLoggedIn) { %>
                            <p class="lead">
                                <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="login" role="button">Login</a>
                                <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="signup" role="button">SignUp</a>
                            </p>
                            <% } else { %>
                            <p class="lead">
                                <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="list" role="button">MyTodos</a>
                            </p>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="sec-about" class="sec-about pt-5 pb-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
                    <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8">
                        <h1 class="h4">About us</h1>
                        <p class="mt-4 mb-4">Twello is a Website that gives people a platform to create Todo lists and
                            also to share their Todo lists with the world on twitter. We want to help peoples those who
                            want to make a change, by helping them to plan and manage themselves and to share their
                            progress with the whole world. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row mt-4">
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <h4>350</h4>

                        <hr />

                        <h5>
                            members</h5>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <h4>60</h4>

                        <hr />

                        <h5>co-working spaces </h5>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <h4>3</h4>

                        <hr />

                        <h5>members' bars</h5>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="sec-features" class="sec-features pt-5 pb-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h2 class="h3">Make Todo Lists</h2>

                        <hr />

                        <p>Create your Todo lists and check-out/edit your lists at any time.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/todos.svg" alt="todoList" class="feature-icon">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/tweet.svg" alt="tweet" class="feature-icon">
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h3 class="h3">Tweet Your Todo Lists</h3>

                        <hr />

                        <p>Planned your Todo list! great! now share the List with the world by tweeting it. Believe us,
                            It will put a healthy pressure on you to complete it.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h3 class="h3">Make your Deadline (comming soon)</h3>

                        <hr />

                        <p>It is better to Create your deadline and stick to it. We shall be helping you with it by
                            tweeting the initial list at the time of creation and tweeting the list at the time of the
                            deadline. It will show the world how much you managed to complete the job.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
                        <img src="/images/completed.svg" alt="deadline" class="feature-icon">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <hr style="width: 100%;">
        <section id="sec-testimonials" class="sec-testimonials mb-5">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="h2 mb-5 text-center">Words from our members</h1>

                <div id="carouselIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                    <!-- <ol class="carousel-indicators">
